|GKO================================================================
                          |RKBBurst
|GKO================================================================

|YKOBurst is the basic attack power of the crinos form. When in a burst,
the crinos form has the potential to do more damage than normal for
a short time. However, this comes at the price of a penalty
to dodge incoming blows.

|RKOSyntax: |YKBburst [<target>]     |WKOCost: |CKO20 sp
